{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c094132407","title":"对习仲勋关于检查绥属各县土地改革情况的报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fcd4262a36","index":0,"year":1948,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"c094132407"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bbc75a90b7","name":"习仲勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3569ff6659","type":"paragraph","text":"对习仲勋关于检查绥属各县土地改革情况的报告的批示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"d343d549ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年1月9日）贺龙，习仲勋及西北局各同志（一）习仲勋同志一月四日给西北局及中央关于边区（老区）进行土改工作的信业已阅悉。（二）我完全同意仲勋同志所提各项意见。望照这些意见密切指导各分区及各县的土改工作，务使边区土改工作循正轨进行，少死错误。（三）提议仲勋同志巡视绥属各县（带一电台联系各地委），明方同志巡视延属各县，每县只住几天，不要耽据太久，并请考虑派文瑞同志（和他将问题说清楚）去三边、陇东、关中巡视一周，是否可行，望的定。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"b7a68e617a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"679c4f0215","type":"paragraph","text":"一月九日[1]习件1月4日向中共中央报告说，苏维埃时期的老区可不采取平分土地的原则，而以抽补办法解决无地和少地农民的土地。如票同新区一上的，又定为地主富农再去斗争，将富裕一点的农民定为地离。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"c040211e06","type":"paragraph","text":"AA中2）美/18","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"b75902865c","type":"paragraph","text":"新恒风两特名国点5者","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"b3ecd685ac","type":"paragraph","text":"相的线西彩点及快送拍也第）这成使图就属素品","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"d2b3589118","type":"paragraph","text":"服务店同志般的差","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"e7b255f365","type":"paragraph","text":"家迎纯保热销镇程方和的。属和维属名利教是动附表","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"17990c5a1c","type":"paragraph","text":"大国考意安场可二体有有容心藏从c","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"},{"id":"29842cb95d","type":"paragraph","text":"一同是两灯莹的e定同美食天研后色起化疾总见刘学东-月1日毛泽东致贺龙、习仲勋等电的手稿","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407"}],"page":{"id":"a5b739eb50","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c094132407","start":503,"end":504}}}},"__N_SSG":true}